column2: TINDAKMALAYSIA NETWORK SERVICES PLT (TINDAK MALAYSIA)
Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2024), Attorney General Chambers, BERNAMA (https://garasi.bernama.com/stories/kuala-kubu-baharu-by-election-2024#candidates)

This is the non-gazetted official results from SPR. Only 40 saluran level data out of 78 are shown due to incompleteness data display during SPR FB Live.  TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
